      <p>
        Create a
        <strong>bold, playful identity</strong>
        for a dog agility brand and blog. The logotype originated on my
        <strong>agility-themed Instagram</strong>
        and was adapted for the website, aligning with the site's green color. The dog illustration
        retains its natural colors to keep the character (<strong>Roi, my red &amp; white Border
          Collie</strong>) authentic.
      </p>
